# ── Auto-generate session-start-contract.compact.md (Tier-0 startup contract) ──
# Canonical compact startup contract shared by all seats.
# Source of truth: brain/MANUAL.md + digest-preamble.md (generated above).
_SESSION_CONTRACT="$BRAIN/brain/index/session-start-contract.compact.md"
